Fannie Mae and Freddie Mac Maximum Loan Limits for Loans Originated in 2009 or 
Originated Between 7/1/07 and 12/31/08 and Purchased in 2009

(These limits were determined under the American Recovery and Reinvestment Act of 2009.  Loans acquired in 2009, but originated prior to 7/1/2007 remain subject to previously-announced 2009 loan limits, which were determined under provisions of the Housing and Economic Recovery Act of 2008).
